Admission Process

Our straightforward application process is designed to help you start your educational journey with ease. Follow these simple steps to begin your path to success.

What You Need to Know

Important information to help you prepare for your application

Required Documents

  • ✓ Valid passport with at least 6 months validity
  • ✓ Academic transcripts and certificates
  • ✓ English language proficiency proof (IELTS/TOEFL)
  • ✓ Personal statement and recommendation letters

Turnaround Times

  • ✓ Application review: 2-3 working days
  • ✓ Offer letter issuance: 1-2 working days
  • ✓ CAS processing time: 5-7 working days
  • ✓ Visa application support: Ongoing

Application Deadlines

  • ✓ January intake: October 15th
  • ✓ May intake: March 15th
  • ✓ September intake: July 15th
  • ✓ Early applications recommended for priority
